{"tid":2497154,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"華航林志玲爆乳出嫁！起底新郎超狂背景「天王愛將」","createTime":"2021-04-20T10:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T10:44:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b68212347ec8899df1bdd3bb6da6a936d6e2960","tid":2497154,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sEPKoJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsEPKoJY.jpg&h=4480a180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被喻為 「華航林志玲」的Kelly（陳詠欣）上周日舉辦婚宴，新郎背景被起底，居然是王<br />\n力宏的貼身愛將廖士元（十元），王力宏當日到場祝賀，滿臉鬍渣模樣相當滄桑。<br />\n<br />\nKelly跟廖士元交往期間多是遠距離關係，Kelly忙著空姐工作，廖士元得陪著王力宏出國<br />\n，負責拍攝、剪接、製作各種影片與平面攝影工作，因此小倆口往往3、4個月見不到面，<br />\n最常約會的地方則是機場。聚少離多的狀況讓兩人一度相當沮喪，前段時間因為疫情緣故<br />\n，交往5年的兩人反而有機會好好相處，也決定互許終身。<br />\n <br />\n在交換誓言時，廖士元引用王力宏「我們的歌」的歌詞：「情人總是分分合合，可是我們<br />\n卻越愛越深。」相當感人。王力宏以「Forever Love」的歌詞祝福佳偶：「你會是所有幸<br />\n福的理由。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HimwXuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHimwXuv.jpg&h=7aad245e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stars.udn.com/star/amp/story/10089/5399818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstars.udn.com%2Fstar%2Famp%2Fstory%2F10089%2F5399818&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=1adbc83a\" target=\"_blank\">https://stars.udn.com/star/amp/story/10089/5399818</a>"},{"pid":"0daf2441b7a57026c41010c41eb89e4304511ee4","tid":2497154,"uid":155012,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:19:07.000Z","msg":"John wick?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e85af240d7b3054c7c089b26f0dad4351d948d","tid":2497154,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"做乜變john wick"},{"pid":"2746d5c25db71e23f7f31300985c44abdb3c751a","tid":2497154,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply